    * vazifasi: buyurtma yaratish
    - POST, "/create_order"
    - header token berasiz
    - body (test ma'lumotlar example berilgan. latitude, longitude, address testoviy ma'lumot berib turasizlar hozircha)
       {
        "ls" : [
            {
                "productID" : 81,
                "count" : 10
            },

            {
                "productID" : 76,
                "count" : 5
            }
        ],
        "latitude" : "41.00",
        "longitude" : "69.00",
        "address" : "TEST"
    }

    * vazifasi: userni buyurtmalari ro'yxatini olish
    - GET,  "/my_orders"
    - headerda token berasiz
    * vazifasi: Userni manzillari ro'yxatini olish
    - GET,  "/address"
    - Header: token

    * vazifasi: Manzil qo'shish
    - POST: "/address/add"
    - header: token
    - body:
       {
           "name" : "TEST",
           "latitude" : 41.2445,
           "longitude" : 69.02213
       }

    * vazifasi: Manzil ma'lumotlarini o'zgartirish
    - POST: "/address/edit"
    - header: token
    - body:
       {
           "id" : 7,
           "name" : "TEST",
           "latitude" : 41.2445,
           "longitude" : 69.02213
       }

    * vazifasi: Manzil ma'lumotini o'chirish
    - POST: "/address/delete"
    - header: token
    - query params: "id"